🔥 🔹 RiskPolicy ke andar kya hota hai?
👉 Ye ek policy object hota hai jo define karta hai:
Risk rules / conditions
Policy violations (SoD etc.)
Risk level / severity
Filters (kis user pe apply hoga)
Actions (violation hone par kya kare)
Risk contribution/scoring
